    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_camp-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "env_adv_2d_camp-00-noon"
    },
    {
      "type": "sfx",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_mountain-01.m4a",
      "startTime": 0
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "hrk",
      "speakerName": "佐伯遙子",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-haruko.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_hrk_51_03/sud_vo_adv_card_hrk_51_03-hrk001.m4a",
      "text": "ふわぁ～……よく寝た～\nあれっ！？　どうして酒瓶が転がってるの！？",
      "startTime": 6.4333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_camp-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "env_adv_2d_camp-00-noon"
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mhk",
      "speakerName": "miho",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-miho.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_hrk_51_03/sud_vo_adv_card_hrk_51_03-mhk001.m4a",
      "text": "んん……何？　朝からうるさいわね\n昨晩、貴方達で空けたんでしょう。私は知らないわよ",
      "startTime": 16.2333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_camp-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "env_adv_2d_camp-00-noon"
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rio",
      "speakerName": "神崎莉央",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rio.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_hrk_51_03/sud_vo_adv_card_hrk_51_03-rio001.m4a",
      "text": "おはよう、二人とも。……もしかして昨日のこと\n何も覚えてないの？　お酒の味も？",
      "startTime": 24.8333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_camp-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "env_adv_2d_camp-00-noon"
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "hrk",
      "speakerName": "佐伯遙子",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-haruko.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_hrk_51_03/sud_vo_adv_card_hrk_51_03-hrk002.m4a",
      "text": "二人からプレゼントにお酒をもらったのは覚えてるわ\n味は、うーん辛口？　いや甘口だったかも……？",
      "startTime": 33.1333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_camp-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "env_adv_2d_camp-00-noon"
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rio",
      "speakerName": "神崎莉央",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rio.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_hrk_51_03/sud_vo_adv_card_hrk_51_03-rio002.m4a",
      "text": "本当に覚えてないの！？\n超高級日本酒セットだったのよ！？",
      "startTime": 42.3999984741,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_camp-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "env_adv_2d_camp-00-noon"
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "hrk",
      "speakerName": "佐伯遙子",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-haruko.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_hrk_51_03/sud_vo_adv_card_hrk_51_03-hrk003.m4a",
      "text": "えーっと、すっごく美味しかったから\nこんなに酔っ払ったのかな～なんて……遙子大失敗",
      "startTime": 48.2999984741,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_camp-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "env_adv_2d_camp-00-noon"
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rio",
      "speakerName": "神崎莉央",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rio.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_hrk_51_03/sud_vo_adv_card_hrk_51_03-rio003.m4a",
      "text": "まったく呆れるわね。こんな大人にならないよう\n今からリズノワのメンバーにも言っておかないと",
      "startTime": 60.2333318074,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_camp-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "env_adv_2d_camp-00-noon"
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mhk",
      "speakerName": "miho",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-miho.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_hrk_51_03/sud_vo_adv_card_hrk_51_03-mhk002.m4a",
      "text": "二日酔いはどうなの？\n私は少し残ってるけど、今日の活動に支障はないわ",
      "startTime": 65.3333318074,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_camp-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "env_adv_2d_camp-00-noon"
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rio",
      "speakerName": "神崎莉央",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rio.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_hrk_51_03/sud_vo_adv_card_hrk_51_03-rio004.m4a",
      "text": "私も全然大丈夫ですよ\n一応、二人とも無理はしないようにね",
      "startTime": 72.4666651408,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_camp-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "env_adv_2d_camp-00-noon"
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "hrk",
      "speakerName": "佐伯遙子",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-haruko.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_hrk_51_03/sud_vo_adv_card_hrk_51_03-hrk004.m4a",
      "text": "ええっ！？　こんなに飲んだのに！？\n莉央さんって実は酒豪なの！？",
      "startTime": 79.3333318074,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_camp-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "env_adv_2d_camp-00-noon"
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rio",
      "speakerName": "神崎莉央",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rio.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_hrk_51_03/sud_vo_adv_card_hrk_51_03-rio005.m4a",
      "text": "そんな訳ないでしょ\n貴方達の介抱で自分が酔うどころじゃなかったわよ……",
      "startTime": 84.0666610718,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_camp-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "env_adv_2d_camp-00-noon"
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "hrk",
      "speakerName": "佐伯遙子",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-haruko.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_hrk_51_03/sud_vo_adv_card_hrk_51_03-hrk005.m4a",
      "text": "ま、まあ二日酔いも、これから行く\n温泉に浸かれば、吹き飛んじゃうと思うし！",
      "startTime": 91.6333277385,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_camp-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "env_adv_2d_camp-00-noon"
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mhk",
      "speakerName": "miho",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-miho.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_hrk_51_03/sud_vo_adv_card_hrk_51_03-mhk003.m4a",
      "text": "温泉？　そんな話してたかしら",
      "startTime": 94.9666544597,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "hrk",
      "speakerName": "佐伯遙子",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-haruko.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_hrk_51_03/sud_vo_adv_card_hrk_51_03-hrk006.m4a",
      "text": "あれ、言ってなかった？　この近くに\n人が全く来ない穴場の秘湯があるのよ！",
      "startTime": 102.4333211263,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_camp-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "env_adv_2d_camp-00-noon"
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "hrk",
      "speakerName": "佐伯遙子",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-haruko.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_hrk_51_03/sud_vo_adv_card_hrk_51_03-hrk007.m4a",
      "text": "今日はそこに寄ってから\n東京に帰るスケジュールになってまーす！",
      "startTime": 107.899987793,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_camp-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "env_adv_2d_camp-00-noon"
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rio",
      "speakerName": "神崎莉央",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rio.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_hrk_51_03/sud_vo_adv_card_hrk_51_03-rio006.m4a",
      "text": "撮影も入らないのよね？\nそれなら、ゆっくり出来そうだわ",
      "startTime": 113.4333211263,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_camp-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "env_adv_2d_camp-00-noon"
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "hrk",
      "speakerName": "佐伯遙子",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-haruko.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_hrk_51_03/sud_vo_adv_card_hrk_51_03-hrk008.m4a",
      "text": "ええ。大人組だけのボーナスタイムよ\n本当にいい所だから、二人も気に入ると思うの",
      "startTime": 119.5666544597,
      "sfxList": [
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_spa-01.m4a",
          "delay": 5266.666666600003,
          "startTime": 124.8333211263
        },
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_sisiodoshi-01.m4a",
          "delay": 5266.666666600003,
          "startTime": 124.8333211263
        },
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_water-02.m4a",
          "delay": 10900.012207000003,
          "startTime": 130.4666666667
        },
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_sisiodoshi-01.m4a",
          "delay": 13566.678873599983,
          "startTime": 133.1333333333
        },
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_water-02.m4a",
          "delay": 17200.012206999985,
          "startTime": 136.7666666667
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_onsenbath-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "env_adv_2d_onsenbath-00-noon"
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_onsenbath-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "env_adv_2d_onsenbath-00-noon"
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_onsenbath-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "env_adv_2d_onsenbath-00-noon"
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mhk",
      "speakerName": "miho",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-miho.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_hrk_51_03/sud_vo_adv_card_hrk_51_03-mhk004.m4a",
      "text": "キャンプ場から意外と近いのね\n昨日と比べて、あっさり着いたわ",
      "startTime": 128.4333134969,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "sfx",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_water-pacha-01.m4a",
      "startTime": 125.1
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rio",
      "speakerName": "神崎莉央",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rio.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_hrk_51_03/sud_vo_adv_card_hrk_51_03-rio007.m4a",
      "text": "ふわぁー、気持ちいい\nお湯もしっとりしてて、肌に良さそうね",
      "startTime": 134.0333165486,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "hrk",
      "speakerName": "佐伯遙子",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-haruko.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_hrk_51_03/sud_vo_adv_card_hrk_51_03-hrk009.m4a",
      "text": "この温泉、美肌効果があるみたいなの\nちょっとの間だけど、ゆっくりしましょうか",
      "startTime": 140.9333134968,
      "sfxList": [
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_sisiodoshi-01.m4a",
          "delay": 4033.3531698999823,
          "startTime": 141.6666666667
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_mountainroad-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "mountainroad-00-noon"
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_mountainroad-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "mountainroad-00-noon"
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "hrk",
      "speakerName": "佐伯遙子",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-haruko.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_hrk_51_03/sud_vo_adv_card_hrk_51_03-hrk010.m4a",
      "text": "大分リフレッシュ出来たわね！\n充電満タン！　って感じよ！",
      "startTime": 149.1666508992,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_mountainroad-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "mountainroad-00-noon"
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mhk",
      "speakerName": "miho",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-miho.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_hrk_51_03/sud_vo_adv_card_hrk_51_03-mhk005.m4a",
      "text": "ええ、悪くなかったわ。貴方が秘湯って言うから\n変な所に連れてかれるのかと思ったけど",
      "startTime": 156.3333175659,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rio",
      "speakerName": "神崎莉央",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rio.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_hrk_51_03/sud_vo_adv_card_hrk_51_03-rio008.m4a",
      "text": "遙子の誕生日企画なのに、なんだか\nおもてなしされてるみたいで、気が引けるわね",
      "startTime": 162.1333175659,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_mountainroad-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "mountainroad-00-noon"
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "hrk",
      "speakerName": "佐伯遙子",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-haruko.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_hrk_51_03/sud_vo_adv_card_hrk_51_03-hrk011.m4a",
      "text": "そんなことないわ。私がみんなで来たかったんだもの",
      "startTime": 165.1666519165,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_mountainroad-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "mountainroad-00-noon"
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "hrk",
      "speakerName": "佐伯遙子",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-haruko.png",
